<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Fiche d'Inscription - <%= student.firstName %> <%= student.lastName %></title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #2c5aa0;
            --secondary-color: #059669;
            --border-color: #cbd5e1;
            --text-dark: #1e293b;
            --text-muted: #64748b;
        }
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            line-height: 1.5;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        @media print {
            body {
                padding: 0;
                background-color: white;
            }
            .no-print {
                display: none !important;
            }
            .page-container {
                box-shadow: none !important;
            }
        }
        
        .page-container {
            background-color: white;
            max-width: 21cm;
            min-height: 29.7cm;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2cm 1.5cm;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        @media print {
            .page-container {
                max-width: 100%;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 1.5cm 1cm;
            }
        }
        
        /* En-tête officiel avec logo */
        .official-header {
            border: 3px solid var(--primary-color);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #f8fafc 0%, white 100%);
        }
        
        .logo-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        
        .logo {
            width: 300px;
            height: 100px;
            object-fit: contain;
            display: block;
        }
        
        .institution-name {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin: 10px 0 5px 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        
        .document-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            margin: 5px 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        .academic-year {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-style: italic;
        }
        
        /* Informations étudiant */
        .student-identity {
            border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            background-color: #fefefe;
        }
        
        .student-details {
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        .student-name {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        .inscription-number {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .student-photo-container {
            margin-left: 25px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .student-photo {
            width: 120px;
            height: 150px;
            border: 3px solid var(--primary-color);
            object-fit: cover;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }
        
        .photo-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-top: 5px;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        
        /* Sections */
        .section-title {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 15px;
            margin: 25px 0 15px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        /* Tableau d'informations */
        .info-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        
        .info-table td {
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }
        
        .info-table td:first-child {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            font-weight: 600;
            width: 35%;
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }
        
        .info-table td:last-child {
            background-color: white;
            width: 65%;
        }
        
        /* Documents */
        .documents-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        
        .document-card {
            border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            background: white;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }
        
        .document-card h6 {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }
        
        .document-image {
            max-width: 100%;
            max-height: 200px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            object-fit: contain;
        }
        
        @media print {
            .documents-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
                gap: 10px;
            }
            .document-image {
                max-height: 800px;
            }
        }
        
        /* Badges de statut */
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 6px 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        .status-pending {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            color: #92400e;
            border: 1px solid #fbbf24;
        }
        
        .status-approved {
            background-color: #d1fae5;
            color: #065f46;
            border: 1px solid #10b981;
        }
        
        .status-rejected {
            background-color: #fee2e2;
            color: #991b1b;
            border: 1px solid #ef4444;
        }
        
        .document-status {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        
        .status-received {
            background-color: #d1fae5;
            color: #065f46;
            border: 1px solid #10b981;
        }
        /* Pied de page avec signatures */
        .footer-section {
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 25px;
            border-top: 3px double var(--border-color);
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }
        
        .signatures-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        
        .signature-box {
            text-align: center;
            width: 45%;
        }
        
        .signature-line {
            border-top: 2px solid var(--text-dark);
            margin: 80px 0 10px 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
        
        .signature-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }
        
        .signature-sublabel {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-style: italic;
        }
        
        /* Note de bas de page */
        .footer-note {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--primary-color);
            font-size: 11px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-style: italic;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="page-container">
        <!-- En-tête officiel -->
        <div class="official-header">
            <div class="logo-wrapper">
                <img src="<%= student.logoUrl || '/logo-write.png' %>" alt="Logo ISA" class="logo">
            </div>
            <div class="document-title">Fiche d'Inscription Étudiant(e)</div>
            <div class="academic-year">Année Académique <%= new Date().getFullYear() %>-<%= new Date().getFullYear() + 1 %></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Identité de l'étudiant avec photo -->
        <div class="student-identity">
            <div class="student-details">
                <div class="student-name"><%= student.firstName %> <%= student.lastName %></div>
                <div class="inscription-number">N° d'Inscription : <%= student.inscriptionId %></div>
                <div style="margin-top: 8px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted);">
                    Date de soumission : <%= new Date(student.submissionDate).toLocaleDateString('fr-FR', {day: '2-digit', month: 'long', year: 'numeric'}) %>
                </div>
                <div class="qr-code">
                    <img src="<%= qrCode %>" alt="QR Code" class="qr-code-image" width="100">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="student-photo-container">
                <% if (student.identityPhoto) { %>
                    <img src="<%= student.identityPhotoUrl || '/api/v1/document?fullPath=' + student.identityPhoto %>" alt="Photo" class="student-photo">
                <% } else { %>
                    <div class="student-photo" style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: #f1f5f9;">
                        <i class="fas fa-user fa-3x" style="color: #94a3b8;"></i>
                    </div>
                <% } %>
                <div class="photo-label">Photo d'identité</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- I. Informations personnelles -->
        <h4 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-user"></i> I. INFORMATIONS PERSONNELLES</h4>
        <table class="info-table">
            <tr>
                <td>Nom complet</td>
                <td><strong><%= student.firstName %> <%= student.lastName %></strong></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Date de naissance</td>
                <td><%= new Date(student.birthDate).toLocaleDateString('fr-FR', {day: '2-digit', month: 'long', year: 'numeric'}) %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Lieu de naissance</td>
                <td><%= student.birthPlace %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Genre</td>
                <td><%= student.gender === 'male' ? 'Masculin' : 'Féminin' %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Numéro CIN</td>
                <td><%= student.cin || 'Non fourni' %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Adresse complète</td>
                <td><%= student.address %></td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <!-- II. Coordonnées -->
        <h4 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> II. COORDONNÉES</h4>
        <table class="info-table">
            <tr>
                <td>Téléphone</td>
                <td><%= student.phone %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Adresse email</td>
                <td><%= student.email %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="2" style="background-color: #e0f2fe; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;">Contact d'urgence</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Nom du contact d'urgence</td>
                <td><%= student.emergencyContactName %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Lien de parenté</td>
                <td><%= student.emergencyContactRelation %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Téléphone d'urgence</td>
                <td><%= student.emergencyContactPhone %></td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <!-- III. Parcours académique -->
        <h4 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i> III. PARCOURS ACADÉMIQUE</h4>
        <table class="info-table">
            <tr>
                <td>Dernier diplôme obtenu</td>
                <td><%= student.lastDiploma %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Série du Baccalauréat</td>
                <td><%= student.bacSeries %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Année d'obtention du BAC</td>
                <td><%= student.bacYear %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Établissement d'origine</td>
                <td><%= student.previousInstitution %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Filière demandée</td>
                <td><strong style="text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--secondary-color);"><%= student.field %></strong></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Niveau d'inscription</td>
                <td><%= student.levelAsked %></td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <!-- IV. Informations administratives -->
        <h4 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-file-invoice"></i> IV. INFORMATIONS ADMINISTRATIVES</h4>
        <table class="info-table">
            <tr>
                <td>Numéro de transaction</td>
                <td><strong><%= student.transactionNumber %></strong></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Acceptation des conditions</td>
                <td>
                    <span class="document-status <%= student.acceptingTerms ? 'status-received' : '' %>" style="<%= !student.acceptingTerms ? 'background: #fee2e2; color: #991b1b; border: 1px solid #ef4444;' : '' %>">
                        <i class="fas fa-<%= student.acceptingTerms ? 'check' : 'times' %>"></i>
                        <%= student.acceptingTerms ? 'Conditions acceptées' : 'Non acceptées' %>
                    </span>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <!-- V. Documents justificatifs -->
        <h4 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-folder-open"></i> V. DOCUMENTS JUSTIFICATIFS</h4>
        
        <% if (student.identityPhoto || student.idDocument || student.residenceCertificate || student.bacTranscript) { %>
            <div class="documents-grid">
                
                <% if (student.idDocument) { %>
                    <div class="document-card">
                        <h6>CARTE D'IDENTITÉ NATIONALE (CIN)</h6>
                        <img src="<%= student.idDocumentUrl || '/api/v1/document?fullPath=' + student.idDocument %>" alt="CIN" class="document-image">
                    </div>
                <% } %>
                
                <% if (student.residenceCertificate) { %>
                    <div class="document-card">
                        <h6>CERTIFICAT DE RÉSIDENCE</h6>
                        <img src="<%= student.residenceCertificateUrl || '/api/v1/document?fullPath=' + student.residenceCertificate %>" alt="Certificat" class="document-image">
                    </div>
                <% } %>
                
                <% if (student.bacTranscript) { %>
                    <div class="document-card">
                        <h6>RELEVÉ DE NOTES DU BACCALAURÉAT</h6>
                        <img src="<%= student.bacTranscriptUrl || '/api/v1/document?fullPath=' + student.bacTranscript %>" alt="Relevé BAC" class="document-image">
                    </div>
                <% } else { %>
                    <div class="document-card" style="border:2px solid #ef4444; background:#fff;">
                        <h6 style="color:#ef4444;">RELEVÉ DE NOTES DU BACCALAURÉAT</h6>
                        <div style="height:120px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;">
                            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle" style="font-size:38px;color:#ef4444;opacity:0.7;"></i>
                        </div>
                        <span class="document-status" style="background:#fee2e2;color:#991b1b;border:1px solid #ef4444;">
                            <i class="fas fa-times"></i> Document manquant
                        </span>
                    </div>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        <% } else { %>
            <div style="padding: 20px; background: #fef3c7; border: 2px solid #fbbf24; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;">
                <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle" style="color: #92400e; font-size: 24px;"></i>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #92400e; font-weight: bold;">Aucun document justificatif fourni</p>
            </div>
        <% } %>

        <!-- Déclaration et signatures -->
        <div class="footer-section">
            <div style="padding: 15px; background: #f8fafc; border: 2px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
                <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.6;">
                    <strong>DÉCLARATION :</strong> Je soussigné(e) <strong><%= student.firstName %> <%= student.lastName %></strong>, 
                    certifie que les informations fournies dans cette fiche d'inscription sont exactes et conformes à la réalité. 
                    Je m'engage à respecter le règlement intérieur de l'Institut Supérieur d'Ambatomirahavavy.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="signatures-container">
                <div class="signature-box">
                    <div style="text-align: right;">
                        <p style="margin: 0 0 5px 0; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold;">Signature de l'étudiant(e)</p>
                        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted);">
                            Fait à ........................, le <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString('fr-FR', {day: '2-digit', month: 'long', year: 'numeric'}) %>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="signature-line"></div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer-note">
            <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
            <strong>Note importante :</strong> Ce document constitue la fiche officielle d'inscription de l'étudiant(e) 
            à l'Institut Supérieur d'Ambatomirahavavy. Il doit être conservé dans le dossier administratif de l'étudiant(e). 
            Toute falsification des informations contenues dans ce document entraînera des sanctions disciplinaires.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>